Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • jgame.entity.Observable
      • jgame.entity.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Camera, GameObject

    public abstract class Entity
extends Observable
    An entity represents every object, example: Game Object, Camera. An entity is NOT a component.
